	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>By Decree</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_HELP">
			<Text>We have promised the people Peace, Land and Bread. Let us deliver.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Supply {1_YieldCost} so that the City's Hospital may generate +4 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The City gains {2_InstantYield}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Sources of [ICON_RES_WHEAT] Wheat worked by the City yield +4 [ICON_FOOD] Food and +2 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>We promised peace. The doctors of this City work overtime to save the war's wounded. Selflessly they help not only their own countrymen, but also those other brothers of Order who have come seeking aid. We need to give them what help we can.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>We promised land. See to it that the lands surrounding the City are hastened into our protection.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_PEACE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>We promised bread. Dispatch our Scientists, that the specimens of Wheat in this City might provide bounty for all!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
